works.description: We have earlier seen a range of racing simulators that combine state-of-the-art technology with cutting-edge design to make for extremely realistic simulations. Here comes the new GT5 Racing Console in carbon fiber from the house of RevoZport. Both the console and seat of the RevoZport GT5 Carbon Driving Console are made of genuine carbon fiber as used in F1 racecars. It has been designed to fit perfectly with the Logitech G25/G27 or Fanatec steering control with perfect foot pedal, gearshift and steering column locking.
